        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued May 1 at 8:18PM CDT by NWS Paducah KY</headline>
        <description>At 818 PM CDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm near
Cedar Lake Area, or 10 miles southwest of Carbondale, moving east at
25 mph.

HAZARD...Penny size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor hail damage to vegetation is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Carbondale, Cobden, Cedar Lake Area, Makanda, and Alto Pass.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
